videos.description: 1H (18:32) WVU Tarik Phillip gathers the ball after the steal and finishes with the Layup.
videos.headline: Tarik Phillip with the atheltic finish at the rim

videos.description: Following a huge Temple Run to expand their lead to 13, WVU coach Bob Huggins makes his displeasure known
videos.headline: Bob Huggins gets called for the technical

videos.description: 2H (14:45) TEM Shizz Alston Jr. made Layup. Assisted by Alani Moore II.
videos.headline: Temple puts on a clinic while beating the West Virginia pressure

videos.description: After some great ball movement, TEM Quinton Rose throws it down
videos.headline: Quinton Rose dunk caps off a great Temple possession

videos.description: Down 20 at half, Myers jumper evens the score for WVU
videos.headline: Teyvon Myers ties it up

videos.description: 2H (3:40) TEM Daniel Dingle takes the defender one on one and finishes with the layup.
videos.headline: Dingle ball-fakes the defender and finishes at the hoop

videos.description: Needing a 3-pointer in the final seconds, Temple's Shizz Alston Jr. makes the block to preserves the win for the Owls.
videos.headline: Temple thwarts last chance for West Virginia

videos.description: Len Elmore and Rich Hollenberg break down the action at the Barclays Center
videos.headline: Post-game recap of NIT Tip-off Championship game that saw Temple prevail over West Virginia
